<?xml version="1.0" encoding="UTF-8"?>
<svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="1400" height="2000" viewBox="0 0 1400 2000">
  <defs>
    <linearGradient id="bg" x1="0" y1="0" x2="1" y2="1">
      <stop offset="0%" stop-color="#f4f9ff"/>
      <stop offset="100%" stop-color="#eef1ff"/>
    </linearGradient>
    <linearGradient id="titleG" x1="0" y1="0" x2="1" y2="0">
      <stop offset="0%" stop-color="#5b7bff"/>
      <stop offset="100%" stop-color="#7e5dff"/>
    </linearGradient>
  </defs>

  <rect x="0" y="0" width="1400" height="2000" fill="url(#bg)"/>

  <rect x="50" y="40" width="1300" height="180" rx="24" fill="url(#titleG)"/>
  <text x="90" y="110" font-size="52" font-family="Arial, Microsoft YaHei" fill="#ffffff" font-weight="700">TrainerSync: Realtime Gym Companion</text>
  <text x="90" y="152" font-size="24" font-family="Arial, Microsoft YaHei" fill="#eaf0ff">CPT208 Human-Centric Computing | Theme C3 Go Trainers | Group C3-6</text>
  <text x="90" y="186" font-size="20" font-family="Arial, Microsoft YaHei" fill="#eaf0ff">Demo URL: https://rainm1st.github.io/</text>

  <rect x="50" y="250" width="410" height="500" rx="18" fill="#ffffff" stroke="#d8e3ff"/>
  <text x="75" y="300" font-size="30" font-family="Arial, Microsoft YaHei" fill="#2a3f8a" font-weight="700">1. Background &amp; Motivation</text>
  <text x="75" y="350" font-size="19" font-family="Arial, Microsoft YaHei" fill="#5a6aa0">Problem: In onsite sessions, coaches cannot monitor</text>
  <text x="75" y="380" font-size="19" font-family="Arial, Microsoft YaHei" fill="#5a6aa0">all trainees simultaneously; trainees lack timely feedback.</text>
  <text x="75" y="425" font-size="19" font-family="Arial, Microsoft YaHei" fill="#5a6aa0">Goal: Build a playful, low-cognitive-load web app for</text>
  <text x="75" y="455" font-size="19" font-family="Arial, Microsoft YaHei" fill="#5a6aa0">realtime coaching and training continuity.</text>
  <text x="75" y="500" font-size="19" font-family="Arial, Microsoft YaHei" fill="#5a6aa0">Stakeholders: Gym trainers, instructors, and trainees.</text>

  <rect x="495" y="250" width="410" height="500" rx="18" fill="#ffffff" stroke="#d8e3ff"/>
  <text x="520" y="300" font-size="30" font-family="Arial, Microsoft YaHei" fill="#2a3f8a" font-weight="700">2. User Research</text>
  <text x="520" y="350" font-size="19" font-family="Arial, Microsoft YaHei" fill="#5a6aa0">Methods: Interviews + competitor analysis + literature.</text>
  <text x="520" y="390" font-size="19" font-family="Arial, Microsoft YaHei" fill="#5a6aa0">Persona A (Trainee): needs clear realtime guidance.</text>
  <text x="520" y="420" font-size="19" font-family="Arial, Microsoft YaHei" fill="#5a6aa0">Persona B (Coach): needs low-friction interventions.</text>
  <text x="520" y="465" font-size="19" font-family="Arial, Microsoft YaHei" fill="#5a6aa0">Journey: warm-up → workout → intervention → recap.</text>
  <text x="520" y="500" font-size="19" font-family="Arial, Microsoft YaHei" fill="#5a6aa0">Key finding: realtime + gamification improves engagement.</text>

  <rect x="940" y="250" width="410" height="500" rx="18" fill="#ffffff" stroke="#d8e3ff"/>
  <text x="965" y="300" font-size="30" font-family="Arial, Microsoft YaHei" fill="#2a3f8a" font-weight="700">3. Core Features</text>
  <text x="965" y="350" font-size="19" font-family="Arial, Microsoft YaHei" fill="#5a6aa0">F1 Realtime Training Feedback Engine</text>
  <text x="965" y="385" font-size="19" font-family="Arial, Microsoft YaHei" fill="#5a6aa0">- Heart-rate zone + stage + progress metrics.</text>
  <text x="965" y="430" font-size="19" font-family="Arial, Microsoft YaHei" fill="#5a6aa0">F2 Smart Training Recommendation</text>
  <text x="965" y="465" font-size="19" font-family="Arial, Microsoft YaHei" fill="#5a6aa0">- Muscle/equipment filters + guided placeholders.</text>
  <text x="965" y="510" font-size="19" font-family="Arial, Microsoft YaHei" fill="#5a6aa0">F3 Pet Companion + Daily Challenge</text>
  <text x="965" y="545" font-size="19" font-family="Arial, Microsoft YaHei" fill="#5a6aa0">- Fixed pet identity, dynamic dumbbell/climb actions.</text>

  <rect x="50" y="790" width="860" height="720" rx="18" fill="#ffffff" stroke="#d8e3ff"/>
  <text x="75" y="840" font-size="30" font-family="Arial, Microsoft YaHei" fill="#2a3f8a" font-weight="700">4. Interface &amp; Interaction Flow</text>
  <rect x="75" y="875" width="810" height="610" rx="14" fill="#f7f9ff" stroke="#d8e3ff"/>
  <text x="100" y="930" font-size="22" font-family="Arial, Microsoft YaHei" fill="#5a6aa0">Insert screenshots here:</text>
  <text x="100" y="965" font-size="20" font-family="Arial, Microsoft YaHei" fill="#5a6aa0">- Trainee dashboard (HR ring, challenge, pet companion)</text>
  <text x="100" y="995" font-size="20" font-family="Arial, Microsoft YaHei" fill="#5a6aa0">- Equipment guidance placeholder section</text>
  <text x="100" y="1025" font-size="20" font-family="Arial, Microsoft YaHei" fill="#5a6aa0">- Coach panel (strategy push, realtime monitoring)</text>

  <rect x="940" y="790" width="410" height="350" rx="18" fill="#ffffff" stroke="#d8e3ff"/>
  <text x="965" y="840" font-size="30" font-family="Arial, Microsoft YaHei" fill="#2a3f8a" font-weight="700">5. Evaluation Plan</text>
  <text x="965" y="890" font-size="19" font-family="Arial, Microsoft YaHei" fill="#5a6aa0">Participants: 6-10 users</text>
  <text x="965" y="920" font-size="19" font-family="Arial, Microsoft YaHei" fill="#5a6aa0">Metrics: SUS, task success, task time</text>
  <text x="965" y="950" font-size="19" font-family="Arial, Microsoft YaHei" fill="#5a6aa0">Week 8: alpha usability test</text>
  <text x="965" y="980" font-size="19" font-family="Arial, Microsoft YaHei" fill="#5a6aa0">Week 10: iteration + final validation</text>

  <rect x="940" y="1160" width="410" height="350" rx="18" fill="#ffffff" stroke="#d8e3ff"/>
  <text x="965" y="1210" font-size="30" font-family="Arial, Microsoft YaHei" fill="#2a3f8a" font-weight="700">6. Business Value</text>
  <text x="965" y="1260" font-size="19" font-family="Arial, Microsoft YaHei" fill="#5a6aa0">- Improve training adherence and retention.</text>
  <text x="965" y="1290" font-size="19" font-family="Arial, Microsoft YaHei" fill="#5a6aa0">- Reduce coach cognitive load in group sessions.</text>
  <text x="965" y="1320" font-size="19" font-family="Arial, Microsoft YaHei" fill="#5a6aa0">- Enable scalable onsite training experience.</text>
  <text x="965" y="1360" font-size="19" font-family="Arial, Microsoft YaHei" fill="#5a6aa0">Next: integrate real media assets and cloud backend.</text>

  <rect x="50" y="1545" width="1300" height="380" rx="18" fill="#ffffff" stroke="#d8e3ff"/>
  <text x="75" y="1600" font-size="30" font-family="Arial, Microsoft YaHei" fill="#2a3f8a" font-weight="700">7. References &amp; Credits</text>
  <text x="75" y="1650" font-size="19" font-family="Arial, Microsoft YaHei" fill="#5a6aa0">Consolvo et al. (CHI 2008), Hamari et al. (HICSS 2014), Sardi et al. (JBI 2017)</text>
  <text x="75" y="1680" font-size="19" font-family="Arial, Microsoft YaHei" fill="#5a6aa0">Brooke (SUS), Bangor et al. (SUS evaluation)</text>
  <text x="75" y="1720" font-size="19" font-family="Arial, Microsoft YaHei" fill="#5a6aa0">Prototype: https://rainm1st.github.io/ | Repo: https://github.com/Rainm1st/Rainm1st.github.io</text>
  <text x="75" y="1750" font-size="19" font-family="Arial, Microsoft YaHei" fill="#5a6aa0">AI usage disclosure and tool citations to be listed in final portfolio references.</text>
</svg>
